{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"507","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"Google響應環保！產品將全面使用再生原料製造","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p>2019/08/06 16:00</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/GOOGLE.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 358px;' /></p>\n\n<p>Google旗下產品Made in google。(翻攝Google)</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p style='margin: 0px;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'><font size='3'><font color='#000000'><span style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>蕭元媚</span><span style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;'> </span><span style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>綜合報導</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;'><span style='margin: 0px;'>&nbsp; </span>/ </span><span style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>美國</span></font></font></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><font color='#000000'><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>為了能夠友善環境、永續發展，</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Google</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>宣布將在</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>2020</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>年起，所有</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>made by google</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>的產品，都將回收材料進行再製，</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>google</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>表示，將會進全力提升產品中再生材料的成分。</span></font></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'><font color='#000000'>&nbsp;</font></span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><strong><font color='#000000'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Google</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>響應環保</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'> 2020</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>拚</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>100%</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>碳平衡</span></font></strong></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'><font color='#000000'>&nbsp;</font></span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><font color='#000000'><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>來自美國的跨國科技公司</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Google</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>，自</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>2016</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>年時創造品牌</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Made in google</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>，順勢推出許多產品，包括</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Pixel</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>手機、</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Google Home</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>智慧喇叭、</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Pixelbook</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>筆電等。</span></font></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'><font color='#000000'>&nbsp;</font></span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><font color='#000000'><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>為了實踐永續的理念，在</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>2017</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>年到</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>2018</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>年間，</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Google</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>將出貨的碳排放量減少</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>40%</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>，這次又再度宣布將會在</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>2020</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>年硬體產品的出貨將達</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>100%</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>碳平衡</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>(carbon neutral)</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>。</span></font></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'><font color='#000000'>&nbsp;</font></span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><strong><font color='#000000'><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>節能再生產品</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'> </span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>回饋弱勢家庭</span></font></strong></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'><font color='#000000'>&nbsp;</font></span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;'><font color='#000000'><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>這項碳平衡的計畫將會節省許多能源，計畫中也提到，會在</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>2023</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>年提供</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>100</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>萬台採用再生塑料製做的節能</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Nest</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>恆溫器給弱勢家庭。將產品回收再生產有許多的阻礙，目前他們決定將材料中的聚脂纖維織物</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>(polyester fabric)</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>，換成使用回收塑膠瓶來的織物，</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 16pt;'>Google</span><span style='margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>的硬體部門為了永續策略，花了兩年